{"tid":1504863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界一齊推9月1號塞機場","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T11:54:56.000Z","uid":89434,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9af70be5ff24ad44a666542d4f2fff805d6e28fc","tid":1504863,"uid":89434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:56:30.000Z","msg":"全世界一齊推 + 開新post洗板!! 唔好俾佢沉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全世界一齊推9月1號塞機場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504779</a><br />\n<br />\n今時今日明顯剩係中聯辦同埋機場先會令政府緊張，搞咁多區分晒人力，個個分晒心，不如集中錫春袋！<br />\n<br />\n入機場三大好處<br />\n<br />\n1.機場最能夠影響香港經濟<br />\n2.機場入邊，警渣唔用得催淚彈或者槍，誤傷遊客，死都唔得掂<br />\n3.近身肉搏先最能夠將人數優勢發揮出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n警渣突然發出不反對通知書！居心叵測！<br />\n<br />\n香港人！<br />\nTHE HONG KONG WAY IS NOT ONLY A SLOGAN OR A GAME! IT IS THE TRUE AND ONLY HONG KONG WAY! <br />\n9月1號！<br />\n塞爆機場路上見！"},{"pid":"931c7fd12cb72b26b284f30ff94f80e2a534610e","tid":1504863,"uid":89434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:59:37.000Z","msg":"推!! 全世界一齊推 + 開新 post 洗板<br />\n<br />\n 全世界一齊推9月1號塞機場<br />\n - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504779</a>"},{"pid":"56b11ad55cd385f427417c5f94d0da2b403f2f42","tid":1504863,"uid":89434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"推!! 全世界一齊推 + 開新 post 洗板<br />\n<br />\n全世界一齊推9月1號塞機場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504863</a>"},{"pid":"6a0e66687e0392e43f359f443036e02e1ea53add","tid":1504863,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" clas